        <p>You can assign a URL path to your community from your Flare target<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Pulse"> (if you have Flare 10.2 or later installed)</MadCap:conditionalText>. This can also be done from the Pulse dashboard (by selecting <span class="Emphasis">Administration &gt; Settings</span> and clicking <span class="Emphasis">Communities</span>), but using the Flare target is recommended.</p>
